---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Blog | Reality Foundation" active="blog">

  <div class="page-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">Blog</p>
    <h1>Notes & Commentary</h1>
    <p>Shorter-form writing from the team: research notes, commentary on developments in synthetic media, and thinking-in-progress that does not yet meet the bar for a formal publication.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Categories -->
  <div style="display:flex; gap:var(--space-2); flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:var(--space-8);">
    <span class="tag" style="cursor:default;">Research notes</span>
    <span class="tag" style="cursor:default;">Policy commentary</span>
    <span class="tag" style="cursor:default;">Event reports</span>
    <span class="tag" style="cursor:default;">Field observations</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Empty state -->
  <div class="empty-state">
    <div style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:var(--space-4); opacity:0.4;">&#9632;</div>
    <h3>First post coming soon</h3>
    <p>We are preparing our first set of posts. Topics will include synthetic media trends, notes from the research programme, and commentary on relevant policy developments.</p>
    <a href="/get-involved" class="btn btn-primary">Get notified</a>
  </div>

  <!-- What to expect -->
  <section class="section" style="margin-top:var(--space-16);">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>What you will find here</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card">
        <p class="card-eyebrow">Research notes</p>
        <h3>Behind the work</h3>
        <p>Informal notes on what we are reading, methodological decisions we are wrestling with, and early results that are not yet ready for formal publication.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="card-eyebrow">Policy commentary</p>
        <h3>Developments we are watching</h3>
        <p>Brief analysis of AI Act provisions, court decisions on digital evidence, and regulatory movements relevant to synthetic media detection.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="card-eyebrow">Field observations</p>
        <h3>Cases in the wild</h3>
        <p>When a notable deepfake, manipulation, or provenance failure makes the news, we will write about what it means technically and what it reveals about the problem.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
